item.description: So what to write… I need a plan of action. There is an application I want to fill out: 1) Look at PhD Website for Systems Science. 2) Ask another person for a reference. 3) Ask a third person for a reference. 4) Write the reference skeleton for Mike to modify. 5) Write personal reference and essay for acceptance. 6) Send GRE scores to school. 7) Make sure transcripts are at school.
